---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Home
seo:
  title: Vandore Heritage | Heritage Property Agency
  description: Tailored representation for heritage properties, refined rentals, and relocating teams across Latvia.
_enabled_editors:
  - visual
  - data
hero:
  eyebrow: Personal agency for meaningful spaces
  headline: Heritage properties stewarded with modern precision
  subheadline: Vandore Heritage aligns curators, craftspeople, and clients to deliver heritage restorations, discreet rentals, and relocation experiences that feel personal from day one.
  cta_label: Start a confidential brief
  cta_url: /contact/
sections:
  - title: Why owners choose Vandore
    description: We balance strategic pricing with thoughtful presentation, curating viewings that protect your time while showcasing the soul of the home.
    points:
      - Dedicated strategist, marketer, and viewing lead for every mandate
      - Tailored documentation and story-driven staging assets within two weeks
      - Weekly insight reports covering engagement, sentiment, and next actions
  - title: Relocation experiences with warmth
    description: Executive teams and households receive concierge-level onboarding, from area discovery to short-let arrangements and cultural briefings.
    points:
      - Curated neighbourhood immersions and lifestyle pairing
      - Rentals matched to team rhythms with hospitality-grade services
      - Cultural intelligence briefings for confident decision-making
  - title: Restoration partnerships
    description: We connect architects, artisans, and conservation experts to realise restorations that honour the original narrative while meeting today's comfort standards.
    points:
      - Conservation-grade project planning
      - Material sourcing with provenance tracking
      - On-site guardianship and reporting
featured_properties:
  heading: Featured properties
  items:
    - slug: heritage-villa-balasta
    - slug: riverside-residences-penthouse
testimonials:
  heading: Trusted by owners and partners
  items:
    - quote: Vandore Heritage took our family estate to market with immense respect. Every buyer was briefed, the narrative was preserved, and expectations were exceeded.
      attribution: Elizabete K., Kipsala residence steward
    - quote: Their relocation program balanced our executive needs with humanity. The result—teams feeling at home from the first week.
      attribution: Andris P., Baltics expansion lead
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow" data-cms-bind="#hero.eyebrow">{{ hero.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1 data-cms-bind="#hero.headline">{{ hero.headline }}</h1>
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.subheadline">{{ hero.subheadline }}</p>
    <a class="cta" href="{{ hero.cta_url }}"><span data-cms-bind="#hero.cta_label">{{ hero.cta_label }}</span></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container grid two">
    {% for section in sections %}
    <article class="card" data-cms-collection="sections" data-cms-item="{{ loop.index0 }}">
      <h2 data-cms-bind="title">{{ section.title }}</h2>
      <p data-cms-bind="description">{{ section.description }}</p>
      <ul>
        {% for point in section.points %}
        <li><span data-cms-bind="points[{{ loop.index0 }}]">{{ point }}</span></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h2 data-cms-bind="#featured_properties.heading">{{ featured_properties.heading }}</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid two">
      {% for item in featured_properties.items %}
      {% set property = properties.bySlug[item.slug] %}
      {% if property %}
      <article class="card" data-cms-collection="properties" data-cms-item="{{ property.slug }}">
        <img src="{{ property.gallery[0] }}" alt="{{ property.title }}" data-cms-bind="gallery[0]">
        <h3 data-cms-bind="title">{{ property.title }}</h3>
        <p class="meta">{{ property.city }}, {{ property.area }}</p>
        <p data-cms-bind="hero.subheadline">{{ property.hero.subheadline }}</p>
        <a class="cta" href="/properties/{{ property.slug }}/"><span data-cms-bind="hero.cta_label">{{ property.hero.cta_label }}</span></a>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 data-cms-bind="#testimonials.heading">{{ testimonials.heading }}</h2>
    <div class="grid two">
      {% for testimonial in testimonials.items %}
      <blockquote class="card" data-cms-collection="testimonials" data-cms-item="{{ loop.index0 }}">
        <p data-cms-bind="quote">{{ testimonial.quote }}</p>
        <p class="meta" data-cms-bind="attribution">{{ testimonial.attribution }}</p>
      </blockquote>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



